Application configuration steps:

Lesson - 05 Setup Karma and Jasmine for testing, setup package.json for install

1) Prepare package.json file and run commands: 
 	- sudo npm install -g karma-cli
 	- npm install karma --save-dev
 	- npm install karma-jasmine --save-dev
 	- sudo npm install
2) Run command: karma init. Last question please answer - no.
3) Please see karma.conf.js file for working settings.
